2
00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:39.080
<b>Outskirts of Sweet City</b>

3
00:01:42.200 --> 00:01:44.160
Jinbe came to help?!

4
00:01:44.160 --> 00:01:46.870
Yeah, I was surprised too.

5
00:01:47.730 --> 00:01:51.530
That's a relief. So Nami-san is okay...

6
00:01:54.380 --> 00:01:58.540
But now, we need to figure out how to meet up with them.

7
00:01:58.540 --> 00:02:02.640
Once they hear you're coming back,
I'm sure they'll be happy.

8
00:02:11.700 --> 00:02:12.860
Goodbye!

9
00:02:13.500 --> 00:02:14.320
Sorry...

10
00:02:14.320 --> 00:02:16.530
we should never have done this!

11
00:02:17.450 --> 00:02:21.720
I'm too ashamed to face Nami-san...

12
00:02:23.520 --> 00:02:28.120
Nami and the others were so worried about you.

13
00:02:28.860 --> 00:02:32.620
And yet, I put them through this terrifying ordeal...

14
00:02:37.630 --> 00:02:39.970
Oh, the rain is stopping.

15
00:02:50.720 --> 00:02:55.070
<b>Rook</b>

16
00:02:55.310 --> 00:02:59.340
<b>Mirro-world</b>

17
00:03:03.030 --> 00:03:04.530
I found it!

18
00:03:04.530 --> 00:03:07.640
You sure?! Chobro!

19
00:03:08.410 --> 00:03:12.250
Do you think they can hear us
through this piece of glass?

20
00:03:12.250 --> 00:03:19.050
The last mirror piece I used to talk to you guys broke on the head of that tree monster, Kingbaum.

21
00:03:23.060 --> 00:03:23.970
It broke!

22
00:03:25.820 --> 00:03:27.390
So...

23
00:03:28.350 --> 00:03:33.150
There should be at least a piece of glass
that connects to this one.

24
00:03:35.610 --> 00:03:38.610
Hey! Luffy!

25
00:03:38.610 --> 00:03:40.400
Hey!

26
00:03:40.400 --> 00:03:42.660
Luffy!

27
00:03:44.570 --> 00:03:48.280
Are you there, Luffy?!

28
00:03:48.280 --> 00:03:49.590
Is that...?

29
00:03:49.590 --> 00:03:51.130
It's Chopper!

30
00:03:51.660 --> 00:03:54.250
Hey!

31
00:03:54.250 --> 00:03:57.540
Answer me if you're there!

32
00:03:57.540 --> 00:03:59.550
Chopper!

33
00:04:00.830 --> 00:04:02.260
Luffy!

34
00:04:02.260 --> 00:04:04.470
Hey!

35
00:04:06.260 --> 00:04:09.390
Luffy! Can you hear me?!

36
00:04:09.390 --> 00:04:11.560
Hey!

37
00:04:11.560 --> 00:04:13.040
Here it is!

38
00:04:13.550 --> 00:04:16.440
This is it! It's a piece of glass!

39
00:04:16.440 --> 00:04:18.190
Can you hear me?!

40
00:04:18.190 --> 00:04:20.570
Why is his voice coming out of a mirror?

41
00:04:20.570 --> 00:04:25.490
It's a long story, but Chopper and the others
are in a mirror dimension.

42
00:04:26.490 --> 00:04:28.740
Are you okay, Chopper?

43
00:04:28.740 --> 00:04:32.960
Oh, Luffy! Thank goodness! You're really there!

44
00:04:34.580 --> 00:04:37.130
Luffy! Is Sanji-kun there too?!

45
00:04:38.250 --> 00:04:40.670
Yeah, he's here!

46
00:04:41.540 --> 00:04:44.880
Sanji-san, I'm glad that you're okay.

47
00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:50.720
How are you guys?

48
00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:56.150
We saved everybody from
inside the mirror, Luffy!

49
00:04:56.150 --> 00:05:00.440
Brook even got copies of the poneglyphs!

50
00:05:00.440 --> 00:05:01.780
Really?!

51
00:05:01.780 --> 00:05:04.360
I'm impressed with you guys!

52
00:05:04.360 --> 00:05:09.580
Y-Your compliment doesn't make me happy, you fool!

53
00:05:11.160 --> 00:05:12.690
You fool!

54
00:05:13.680 --> 00:05:15.620
You silly little goose!

55
00:05:16.460 --> 00:05:21.750
Luffy, it's good that Sanji's there,
but did you two come to an agreement?

56
00:05:30.390 --> 00:05:33.560
Sanji isn't... coming back yet.

57
00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:36.270
What?!

58
00:05:51.120 --> 00:05:53.910
Listen, everyone.

59
00:05:53.910 --> 00:05:58.200
We're gonna crash Big Mom's tea party and the wedding.

60
00:05:58.200 --> 00:06:01.000
And we're gonna save Sanji's family!

61
00:06:01.000 --> 00:06:04.380
And then, Sanji will leave with us!

62
00:06:10.170 --> 00:06:13.560
B... Big...

63
00:06:20.440 --> 00:06:23.480
Luffy! She's an emperor!

64
00:06:25.030 --> 00:06:30.280
I don't want to risk everyone's...
I mean, Nami-san's life over my own personal issues!

65
00:06:30.740 --> 00:06:31.700
So...

66
00:06:39.330 --> 00:06:42.250
Yay!

67
00:06:46.340 --> 00:06:48.050
Damn you!

68
00:06:48.050 --> 00:06:53.970
I heard you and Luffy got into a big fight,
so I was worried, you idiot!

69
00:06:53.970 --> 00:06:58.350
I'm so relieved! Really, you idiot!

70
00:06:58.350 --> 00:07:00.980
You big idiot!

71
00:07:00.980 --> 00:07:05.480
If we do that, then Sanji-kun will
leave with us, right, Luffy?!

72
00:07:09.860 --> 00:07:12.450
Nami-san... I...

73
00:07:12.450 --> 00:07:15.080
Oh, Sanji-kun.

74
00:07:15.080 --> 00:07:19.500
For scaring me like you did...

75
00:07:21.240 --> 00:07:23.540
I will never forgive you!

76
00:07:27.540 --> 00:07:28.710
Nami...

77
00:07:32.860 --> 00:07:37.520
But we can talk about that later.
The tea party is soon.

78
00:07:37.520 --> 00:07:41.480
I'm gonna help bring you back no matter what, Sanji-kun!

79
00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:47.080
What?! Are you proposing to me, Nami-san ?!

80
